title: Joel Fameyeh: Local Black Stars striker confident about 2016 CHAN qualification
text:
Sports News | 23 October 2015 11:25 CET Joel Fameyeh: Local Black Stars striker confident about 2016 CHAN qualification - www.ghanasoccernet.com Joel Fameyeh 
Teenage sensation Joel Fameyeh insists the local Black Stars have the quality to reach the finals of the 2016 CHAN finals at the expense of Ivory Coast. 
The tie is delicately poised after Ghana managed a slim 2-1 win over the Elephants last week in Kumasi.
